Author: S3cco
Title: [ANN][ICO+Bounty] Midex | Financial platform with LICENSED exchange
Body: Bitcoin Garden: Midex Launches the First EU Regulated Crypto-to-Fiat Exchange https://bitcoingarden.org/midex-launches-the-first-eu-regulated-crypto-to-fiat-exchange/  Midex, an international company with HQs in Estonia and representatives in Asia, has announced the launch of the first EU regulated crypto-to-fiat exchange. With the trading performance of millions of operations per second, a wide range of deposit and withdrawal methods (wire transfers, payment cards, instant payments), support of the top trading pairs, and a robust security system, the platform is here to meet the needs of crypto beginners and professional traders.  The key pillars of the Midex exchange are legality and safety. Midex is the cryptocurrency exchange that has obtained a termless operating license with the number one (FVR000001), allowing it to provide services of exchanging virtual currencies to the fiat and vice versa.  Moreover, the platform has developed an advanced security system, according to which the main assets are stored in cold wallets, where the private keys are presented as multi-sig, hence, not a single person in the company is able to access e-wallet at any time. Keys have never been performed to the devices or connected to the web, and are stored in geographically distributed locations. The Midex alert system blocks any operations in case of violation of database integrity or an unauthorized change.  When it comes to the crypto-to-fiat exchange, the ability to easily deposit and withdraw funds are a sticking point for many platforms. Midex already launches with such payment options as bank transfer and cards (VISA, MasterCard, and JCB). In the beginning, most of the deposit methods are free of charge....

Author: Midex
Title: [ANN][ICO+Bounty] Midex | Financial platform with LICENSED exchange
Body: Hey there!  July 3, at 15:00 UTC, registration and trading on Midex exchange will be opened.  We are launching our exchange in beta-testing mode. During this period, developers will be testing functions and getting feedback from the community.  All users need to complete the registration process to trade on the Midex exchange. Users who already have an account need to complete the registration again.  There are two ways to deposit your mdx tokens into Midex exchange: 1) Transfer through the ICO account 2) Transfer via MyEtherWallet  Your individual exchange wallet address will be generated when you request to add coins to your balance.   In both cases, you need to have a little amount of ETH in your account, which will be used to pay the commission of ETH network.  MoneyPolo. To activate fiat deposit and withdrawal through the MoneyPolo, it is necessary to pass verification on the web page of the service https://moneypolo.com - this is a must condition.  Please pay attention to our commissions and limits. They are represented on the page of every currency pair.  You can ask your questions in our official chat in Telegram https://t.me/midex_eng or by mail support@midex.com     Thank you for your participation! Lets MIDEX IT!

Author: Midex
Title: [ANN][ICO+Bounty] Midex | Financial platform with LICENSED exchange
Body: Midex is launching exchange in beta-testing.  The first innovative cryptocurrency financial platform of Midex starts beta-testing. Public registration for participation in service testing opens on Tuesday, July 3.  During the testing period all main facilities of the exchange will be operating. The main difference is that all additional services will start operating in August. Some fiat currency pairs will be unavailable during the testing period. Users will be able to deposit or withdraw funds only through the MoneyPolo service.  Full working service will be available in August. Developers are testing functions and getting feedback of the community during July.  During testing period 42 currency pairs will be available for operations: MDX/BTC MDX/ETH MDX/USD MDX/EUR MDX/GBP MDX/JPY MDX/CNY BTC/USD BTC/EUR BTC/GBP BTC/JPY BTC/CNY ETH/BTC ETH/USD ETH/EUR ETH/GBP ETH/JPY ETH/CNY LTC/MDX LTC/ETH LTC/BTC LTC/USD LTC/EUR LTC/GBP LTC/JPY LTC/CNY DASH/MDX DASH/ETH DASH/BTC DASH/USD DASH/EUR DASH/GBP DASH/JPY DASH/CNY NANJ/MDX NANJ/ETH NANJ/BTC NANJ/USD NANJ/EUR NANJ/GBP NANJ/JPY NANJ/CNY     Thank you for your participation! Title: [ANN][ICO+Bounty] Midex | Financial platform with LICENSED exchange
Body: Friends! There is one week after the end of the Midex Tokensale.  The Midex Tokensale is over after 90 days. Within this period, 20 million tokens were sold at a price between $1 and $1.2 and the number of transactions on the site reached 7 million.  Some words about Tokensale period. According to CEO of Midex Dmitry Machikhin, the availability of a working product — a licensed cryptocurrency exchange, a presence of a powerful international team and transparent company structure allowed for a successful Tokensale. In the last month, there were MDX tokens sold instantly. In addition, during Tokensale, Midex visited 20 cities in different countries of the world (including the US, Great Britain, Singapore, Japan, Hong Kong), to meet with the community, investors, partners, and regulators.  Join to our community to keep abreast of the actual news: Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/midexinfo Telegram chat https://t.me/midex_eng Telegram channel https://t.me/midexinfo_en Reddit https://www.reddit.com/user/Midex_Official Twitter https://twitter.com/Lets_Midex_It Medium https://medium.com/@midexofficial Instagram https://www.instagram.com/midexinfo/  Here we are, #midexing for your future!

Author: Midex
Title: [ANN][ICO+Bounty] Midex | Financial platform with LICENSED exchange
Body: We have 3 ways of purchasing tokens:  1. Direct transaction of ETH to smart contract address. 2. Cryptocurrency (not ETH) transaction to shown addresses in account. 3. Transaction from your ETH wallet on our website.  Only using 3rd way you need to type your private key. It is voluntarily. The key is needed to sign your transaction and we don't save or watch your key. These method is MyEtherWallet website analogue. It works the following way: There is a cryptocurrency node for Etherium. So the node is the distribution programm packages which are provided by ETH developers. Any website including Midex refers to that node by API to transfer transaction which afterwards sends to blockchain. On the moment of sending the transaction from website to the node it is necessary to sign up the transaction by your private key. Transaction is signed and send. During this process your private key is not sending anywhere and the transaction is sending already encrypted. This way of payment is made for your convenience and Midex account don't save your private key as well as any other keys. The account is only the tool for displaying of wallets ballances and a guide for token purchasing.  So if if you don't like 3rd way you can buy our tokens by another 2 ways.

Title: [ANN][ICO+Bounty] Midex | Financial platform with LICENSED exchange
Body: We have 3 ways of purchasing tokens:  1. Direct transaction of ETH to smart contract address. 2. Cryptocurrency (not ETH) transaction to shown addresses in account. 3. Transaction from your ETH wallet on our website.  Only using 3rd way you need to type your private key. It is voluntarily. The key is needed to sign your transaction and we don't save or watch your key. These method is MyEtherWallet website analogue. It works the following way: There is a cryptocurrency node for Etherium. So the node is the distribution programm packages which are provided by ETH developers. Any website including Midex refers to that node by API to transfer transaction which afterwards sends to blockchain. On the moment of sending the transaction from website to the node it is necessary to sign up the transaction by your private key. Transaction is signed and send. During this process your private key is not sending anywhere and the transaction is sending already encrypted. This way of payment is made for your convenience and Midex account don't save your private key as well as any other keys. The account is only the tool for displaying of wallets ballances and a guide for token purchasing.

In other side many business owners want to work with cryptocurrencies because they have very convenient, secure and cheap transaction system.
